window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Previously published as </b><b><i>Rain Fall</i></b></p> <p>Name: John Rain.</p> <p>Vocation: Assassin.</p> <p>Specialty: Natural Causes.</p> <p>Base of operations: Tokyo.</p> <p>Availability: Worldwide.&nbsp;</p> <p>Half American, half Japanese, expert in both worlds but at home in neither, John Rain is the best killer money can buy. You tell him who. You tell him where. He doesnâ€™t care about why...</p> <p>Until he gets involved with Midori Kawamura, a beautiful jazz pianist - and the daughter of his latest kill.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>A Clean Kill in Tokyo</i> was previously published as <i>Rain Fall</i>, the first in the bestselling John Rain assassin series.</p>"; 
